flowchart LR
    subgraph Sources
      SCM[Git hosting]
      PM[Issue and planning]
      IDE[IDE and agent telemetry]
      AI[AI coding and review]
      CI[CI and test systems]
      CD[Deployment systems]
      OBS[Production observability]
    end

    SCM --> BUS[Event ingestion]
    PM --> BUS
    IDE --> BUS
    AI --> BUS
    CI --> BUS
    CD --> BUS
    OBS --> BUS

    BUS --> RAW[Immutable event store]
    BUS --> STREAM[Stream processing]
    RAW --> BATCH[Batch and graph processing]
    STREAM --> STATE[Lifecycle state]
    BATCH --> GRAPH[Engineering knowledge graph]
    BATCH --> FEATURES[Versioned feature store]
    STATE --> FEATURES
    GRAPH --> FEATURES

    FEATURES --> METRICS[Metric engine]
    FEATURES --> MODELS[Statistical and ML models]
    METRICS --> EXP[Experiment analysis]
    MODELS --> EXP
    EXP --> DECISIONS[Decision products and dashboards]
    DECISIONS --> REG[Experiment and policy registry]
    REG --> BUS
